basic.description:
{Basic Scouting}

Basic Scouting increases the hero's scouting radius by 1 tile.

It reveals additional information about the foes in the tavern for the hero's owner and allies, as if the team had 1 additional Tavern.

advanced.description:
{Advanced Scouting}

Advanced Scouting increases the hero's scouting radius by 2 tiles.

It reveals additional information about the foes in the tavern for the hero's owner and allies, as if the team had 2 additional Taverns.

expert.description:
{Expert Scouting}

Expert Scouting increases the hero's scouting radius by 3 tiles.

It reveals additional information about the foes in the tavern for the hero's owner and allies, as if the team had 3 additional Taverns.
